In a message dated 2/19/03 12:43:51 AM Central Standard Time, 
airly2002@... writes:


> "Then, my dear Maxima"replied Hydras"YOur mission is clear, but you 
> will need a little help to find my spy, or he finds you..."

"Very well." This would be a difficult task. But.. doable. 

Now.. she awaited & plotted what to do next. 

But... she didn't want to leave. Well... at least not yet. Her optics went to 
him again. "tell me.. more about how you became yourself?" she was curious. 
Sometimes overly curius. But Hydras fascinated her. As to why? the fact that 
he was Megatron & Galvatron.  

--part1_135.1b4fd450.2b8482f2_boundary
